- README badge/footer: 2.0.0 -> 2.0.1
- CHANGELOG: split v2.0.1 into its own entry (was duplicating v2.0.0 content),
  documenting the actual delta (converters, LocalizationService, AppSettingsStore,
  dark mode redesign); v2.0.0 rewrite content kept under its own heading
